{"tid":696112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術] 做風水佬既宿命 係咪真係注定會有絕後，橫禍，破產 三者其一?","createTime":"2018-06-09T19:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-10T04:38:30.000Z","uid":7374,"like":27,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd9c9cfba7ff2989be5aaec4fa37be816b30641","tid":696112,"uid":7374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T19:05:53.000Z","msg":"之前聽過有風水佬講，如果要幫人占掛算命睇風水，並要以此黎搵食既話，就必需係絕後，橫禍，破產呢三種下場，選一種，你睇下而家既風水佬，陳振聰破產，鄭國強比山泥活埋，李丞責老豆本身無仔生，要到七十幾歲擺左個無敵生仔陣先生到李丞責，蘇文峰果D直頭連婚都唔結。可想而知呢D絕後，橫禍，破產真係風水佬既宿命。個風水佬話因為幫人算命，係泄漏天機，你仲要用既黎賺錢既話，其實好傷陰德，所以先會有咁樣既宿命。"},{"pid":"048193a82699af239298c3acf3c023d3b55e145d","tid":696112,"uid":4281,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:44:38.000Z","msg":"麥玲玲？楊天命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231f0cf3b29405bda80d2e88cec52c71d1574757","tid":696112,"uid":35296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"048193a82699af239298c3acf3c023d3b55e145d","tid":696112,"uid":4281,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:44:38.000Z","msg":"麥玲玲？楊天命？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:53:20.000Z","msg":"完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567c33cdd56ce4cc83f86f425b6d3b4a2ed6c977","tid":696112,"uid":44073,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c09faf14eb0ffd1e00a13b32d3d02a082ef1214d","tid":696112,"uid":115510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:54:18.000Z","msg":"真係得個d會"},{"pid":"f286087c01435356060a7a3fd3a672669f2076eb","tid":696112,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:54:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f60405935a27f693d9a4fa5399757434c9315b98","tid":696112,"uid":44073,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T20:56:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}